name: owls are not what they seem
description:
I was inspired by the legendary Twin Peaks. I saw an incomplete owl sign in the branches, and my mind drew a complete picture.
The series first aired in the U.S. on April 8, 1990. So I made 1990 digital copies. After a while, I will burn the unsold leftovers in honor of the sequel to "Twin Peaks. Fire Walk With Me."

Location: Kharkiv, Ukraine
Date of photo creation: March 21, 2021
JPEG is 6000x4000 pixels
